<div class="font-bodyFont flex flex-col items-center gap-9">
    <h2 class="text-3xl">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-primary tracking-wider">At <span class="text-black">DriftDreams</span>
        , we value your inquiries and strive to provide
        the best support possible. Whether you have a query about our products, need guidance, or simply want to
        share your
        thoughts, we're all ears!
        Feel free to ask us anything by filling out the form below. No question is too big or too small. Our
        dedicated team is committed to addressing your concerns promptly and thoroughly.
        Your satisfaction is our priority. So, don't hesitate and reach out to us today!
    </p>
    <form action="" class="my-20 flex flex-col gap-10 items-center">
        <div class="flex gap-10">
            <div class="inputContact">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input required class="p-5 border-2 border-primary" type="email" id="email"
                    placeholder="Enter your email...">
            </div>
            <div class="inputContact">
                <label for="name">Name</label>
                <input required class="p-5 border-2 border-primary" type="text" id="name"
                    placeholder="Enter your name...">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inputContact">
            <label for="message">Message</label>
            <textarea required class="message border-2 border-primary p-4 resize-x" name="" cols="30"
                rows="10"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button class="btn bg-black text-white uppercase">send</button>
        <div class="messageContact messageSuccess opacity-0">
            <p>Message sent</p>
        </div>
    </form>
    <script src="/javascript/messageContact.js"></script>
</div>